				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Thu, 16 Jul 2020 20:19:51 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>MovingCitizen</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>6416381</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I also find myself torn about not labeling this -EX, but at the end of the day the well written and smooth transition from a normal SCP into -EX *and* that very last sentence at the end are what made this SCP click for me. +1 for sure</p> 
				 	]]>
